            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-861446792" class="vote-count">4</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-861446792" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="861446792">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4400048/">章句小楷</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-11-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">蛮有意思。士族寒族儒家法家的路线问题，导致三国的不同走向。这种马列历史观，划分阶级立场的观点倒是第一次听说。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="984485525">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-984485525" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-984485525" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="984485525">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2744950/">七月不远</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">基本上就是说三国的缩水版，基本的分析框架没有变。乍看是很有道理，比如士族与寒族，本地集团与外来集团。但其实细想也经不起推敲，这大概就是试图用单一框架分析复杂问题总是会有这种问题。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
