                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-10-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">以为是满汉全席，结果是青菜豆腐，说好听点就是开门见山，难听就是裤子脱了给我看这个？山是见到了，却没法攀登。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1005567645">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1005567645" class="vote-count">0</span>
